[SN]TITLE[SN]
Artlink gallery searches for Hull trawlermen's vintage suits

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
A Hull gallery is searching for vintage hand-made suits worn by Hull's trawlermen from the 1950s to the mid-1970s.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
